00:03:01.910 --> 00:03:01.920
this—and

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:03.470
we don't tell our business to

00:03:03.480 --> 00:03:05.270
everybody about

00:03:05.270 --> 00:03:05.280
everything—but

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:06.949
she

00:03:06.959 --> 00:03:08.870
has a Master's degree in accounting and

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:10.070
in business.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:11.910
She graduated top of her class. I

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.190
was proud of her. I wanted to show her

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:15.470
awards. She got her Summa Cum Laude

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:18.430
awards. She got all her awards from ORU.

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:21.750
She got her degree in

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:24.509
accounting. She is very educated, and

00:03:24.519 --> 00:03:26.190
she graduated top of her class as she

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:28.030
got awards and everything.

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:29.790
So, I want you to know a lot of times

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:32.630
it's not that she is trying to avoid

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.070
prayer with everybody. Why is Diana not

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:37.110
here? How come she doesn't want to be a

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:40.229
part? She's working a full-time job.

00:03:40.239 --> 00:03:42.430
She's very

00:03:42.440 --> 00:03:44.790
educated. She's been working at this for

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:46.590
years. And I didn't want her to give up

00:03:46.600 --> 00:03:49.430
her career of what she was doing, selling

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:52.110
on eBay and Poshmark and doing the

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:55.350
things that she has done for this. We

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:57.510
don't depend on the ministry for

00:03:57.520 --> 00:04:01.790
finances. My wife works full-time.

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:04.750
I do YouTube. We have a ministry

00:04:04.760 --> 00:04:07.230
property. The ministry has purchased a

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:09.910
ministry property. That's different. I'm

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:11.470
going to be straight up front with you.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:13.270
That is totally different. We did buy a

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:15.790
ministry property.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:18.310
So, it's not shocking and all. When you

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:20.150
have as much coming through, when you

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.910
have this many people coming through,

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:23.790
money flows through here. And I'm

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.190
going to tell you this: I have never

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:27.590
taken a vow of poverty. I'm not afraid

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.670
of what I have. I'm not ashamed of what

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.350
I have. I'm going to tell you this: I

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:33.710
was instructed by the FBI

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:36.790
to get a safe haven for me and my family

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:39.190
because I've had threats on my life all

00:04:39.200 --> 00:04:43.070
the time on a consistent basis.

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:45.950
Where we were at our old house,

00:04:45.960 --> 00:04:48.510
we have people showing up

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:50.790
knocking on our door. And I'm going to

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:52.990
tell you this: when you have

00:04:52.990 --> 00:04:53.000
an

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:55.230
audience like we do and the people that

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:57.550
hate us as much as they do,

00:04:57.550 --> 00:04:57.560
I

00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:59.390
just want to tell you, I

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:02.310
have to protect my family. Now,

00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:04.470
we have attorneys. We've had to hire

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:06.510
full-time security. We're having to look

00:05:06.520 --> 00:05:09.070
