00:05:09.080 --> 00:05:11.190
over me because of the incidents, but

00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:13.310
because of what I've been told by

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:13.320
the

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:15.070
sheriff's department, local law

00:05:15.080 --> 00:05:17.790
enforcement, and the FBI, I must

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:20.990
provide protection for my family because

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.230
of these threats, and they tell me

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:24.870
