00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:46.750
leave and go stay in a hotel that night,

00:05:46.760 --> 00:05:48.950
it's because the Lord's warning me to.

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:52.870
I've had crazy people stay at IHOP for

00:05:52.870 --> 00:05:52.880
seven

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:56.230
