00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:07.150
And I'm just being quite frank;

00:06:07.150 --> 00:06:07.160
I

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.630
don't ever talk about it. We

00:06:08.630 --> 00:06:08.640
don't

00:06:08.640 --> 00:06:10.030
