00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:19.750
okay?

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:22.150
There are a lot of people that hate me.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:25.190
Yes. And you have no idea what happens

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:26.550
